%B8%83%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%A4"><span class="toc-number">7.4.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">开启发布确认</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%AA%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%A4%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83"><span class="toc-number">7.4.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">单个确认发布</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%89%B9%E9%87%8F%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%A4"><span class="toc-number">7.4.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">批量发布确认</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%BC%82%E6%AD%A5%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%A4%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83"><span class="toc-number">7.4.4.</span> <span class="toc-text">异步确认发布</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%BC%82%E6%AD%A5%E6%9C%AA%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%A4%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86"><span class="toc-number">7.4.5.</span> <span class="toc-text">异步未确认消息的处理</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%B9%B3%E8%B0%83%E5%BA%A6"><span class="toc-number">7.5.</span> <span class="toc-text">不公平调度</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-1"><a class="toc-link" href="#Publish-Subscribe"><span class="toc-number">8.</span> <span class="toc-text">Publish&#x2F;Subscribe</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E4%BA%A4%E6%8D%A2%E6%9C%BA%EF%BC%88Exchanges%EF%BC%89"><span class="toc-number">8.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">交换机（Exchanges）</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%97%A0%E5%90%8D%E4%BA%A4%E6%8D%A2%E6%9C%BA"><span class="toc-number">8.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">无名交换机</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E4%B8%B4%E6%97%B6%E9%98%9F%E5%88%97"><span class="toc-number">8.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">临时队列</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></div></div></div></div></main><footer id="footer" style="backg